      "text": "Ride (model)\n- RideID\n- riderId\n- fare\n- ETA\n- src\n- dest\n- status: \"fare-estimated\" | matched | in-ride\n- (.... => can see if there is more fields we want to add here)\n\n\n- ...metadata(i.e. payment info) => will be linked with a foregin key",
